'''Ilavarasi''' is an Indian actress. She has appeared in [[Tamil language|Tamil]], [[Telugu language|Telugu]], [[Malayalam]] and [[Kannada]] languages. She is best known for her supporting roles as well as lead roles of the 1980s. Her popular roles are the one in ''[[Hitler (1996 film)|Hitler]]'' along with [[Mammootty]] and [[Visu]]' s ''[[Samsaram Adhu Minsaram]]''. She is prominently known as Kalpana in Telugu and Manjula Sharma in Kannada.

